  <div class="views-field-field-library-file-fid">
                <div class="field-content"></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p>China‚Äôs Information Office of the State Council recently issued a white paper titled <a href="http://www.china.org.cn/government/whitepaper/node_7172407.htm">‚ÄúChina‚Äôs Policies and Actions for Addressing Climate Change (2012)‚Äù</a>, made available in the run-up to the UNFCCC international negotiations on climate change currently underway in <a href="http://unfccc.int/meetings/doha_nov_2012/meeting/6815.php">Doha, Qatar</a>.</p></div>
