                <span class="field-content"><a href="../blog-posts/indian-chinese-environmental-relations-year-tiger">Indian-Chinese Environmental Relations in the Year of the Tiger</a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-field-image-fid">
                <span class="field-content"><img src="../files/chinainfo/imagecache/news-image/tiger&#32;close&#32;up&#32;blog&#32;15.jpg" alt="" title="" width="169" height="120" class="imagecache imagecache-news-image imagecache-default imagecache-news-image_default"/></span>
